<bibRefCitation author="Danzig, E. M. &amp; Gavrilov-Zimin, I. A." box="[430,845,1270,1294]" firstAuthor="Danzig" journalOrPublisher="Fauna of Russia and Neighbouring Countries. New Series" pageId="1" pageNumber="144" pagination="1 - 678" part="418" refId="ref1028" refString="Danzig, E. M. &amp; Gavrilov-Zimin, I. A. (2014) Palaearctic mealybugs (Homoptera: Coccinea: Pseudococcidae). Part 1. Subfamily Phenacoccinae. Fauna of Russia and Neighbouring Countries. New Series, 418, 1 - 678." title="Palaearctic mealybugs (Homoptera: Coccinea: Pseudococcidae). Part 1. Subfamily Phenacoccinae" type="journal article" year="2014">Danzig &amp; Gavrilov-Zimin (2014: 64)</bibRefCitation>
