<bibRefCitation author="Gavrilov-Zimin, I. A." box="[860,1171,1270,1294]" firstAuthor="Gavrilov-Zimin" journalOrPublisher="Zoosystematica Rossica, Supplementum" pageId="1" pageNumber="144" pagination="1 - 260" part="2" refId="ref1235" refString="Gavrilov-Zimin, I. A. (2018) Ontonogenesis, morphology and higher classification of archaeococcids [Homoptera: Coccinea: Orthezioidea]. Zoosystematica Rossica, Supplementum 2, 1 - 260." title="Ontonogenesis, morphology and higher classification of archaeococcids [Homoptera: Coccinea: Orthezioidea]" type="journal article" year="2018">Gavrilov-Zimin (2018: 208)</bibRefCitation>
